### Admin Login
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@mail.com",
  "password": "admin"
}

### Get All Users (Admin Dashboard)
GET http://localhost:4000/admin/users
Cookie: token=YOUR_ADMIN_COOKIE

### Block User
PATCH http://localhost:4000/admin/users/USER_ID/status
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: token=YOUR_ADMIN_COOKIE

{
  "isUserActive": false
}

### Unblock User
PATCH http://localhost:4000/admin/users/USER_ID/status
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: token=YOUR_ADMIN_COOKIE

{
  "isUserActive": true
}

### Get All Articles (Admin Feed)
GET http://localhost:4000/admin/articles?page=1&limit=10
Cookie: token=YOUR_ADMIN_COOKIE

### Delete Article Permanently
DELETE http://localhost:4000/admin/articles/ARTICLE_ID
Cookie: token=YOUR_ADMIN_COOKIE

### Get Platform Stats
GET http://localhost:4000/admin/stats
Cookie: token=YOUR_ADMIN_COOKIE

### Try Access Without Token
GET http://localhost:4000/admin/users

### Try Admin API with USER login token
GET http://localhost:4000/admin/users
Cookie: token=USER_COOKIE

### Large dataset pagination test
GET http://localhost:4000/admin/articles?page=2&limit=5
Cookie: token=YOUR_ADMIN_COOKIE

